title: Niels-Henning Ørsted Pedersen's solo on Au Privave + Why you should learn Bebop
description:
NHOP's Brilliant Solo on Au Privave, lifted from the Oscar Peterson Trio album 'Nigerian Marketplace'. It made me reflect on the value of learning the bebop language, transcribing in general and how to incorporate transcriptions into your own playing.

Transcription here:  https://www.pwfarrell.com/?p=2807
